    "description": "Last Dawn is a short first-person exploration game set in the year 2082. While attempting to flee a dystopian city, your ship was shot down. You awake in a cold wasteland known as the Old World. You must find a way out, but be careful. You are not alone here.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284090/extras/46039d56107fea34813019470006f959.poster.avif?t=1676311240\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284090/extras/46039d56107fea34813019470006f959.webm?t=1676311240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284090/extras/46039d56107fea34813019470006f959.mp4?t=1676311240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FIND THE TERMINALS</h2>You will have to find the five terminals and deactivate them to escape. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284090/extras/0ec4a428401b162d3af52559f28b1384.poster.avif?t=1676311240\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284090/extras/0ec4a428401b162d3af52559f28b1384.webm?t=1676311240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284090/extras/0ec4a428401b162d3af52559f28b1384.mp4?t=1676311240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HIDE</h2>You will be hunted by the city's android guards. Avoid being spotted and captured. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284090/extras/9d85673b56b3625e857326007d5aba93.poster.avif?t=1676311240\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284090/extras/9d85673b56b3625e857326007d5aba93.webm?t=1676311240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284090/extras/9d85673b56b3625e857326007d5aba93.mp4?t=1676311240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RUN</h2>If you are spotted the guards will run after you and attempt to capture you. It's best to run and find another way around them. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284090/extras/baad9e53c4c85baa0f1b815c2511b678.poster.avif?t=1676311240\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284090/extras/baad9e53c4c85baa0f1b815c2511b678.webm?t=1676311240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284090/extras/baad9e53c4c85baa0f1b815c2511b678.mp4?t=1676311240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ESCAPE</h2>Once all five terminals are deactivated the door will open, allowing you to escape.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284090/extras/f58729f63a58d866f173e6ca6b8f414c.poster.avif?t=1676311240\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284090/extras/f58729f63a58d866f173e6ca6b8f414c.webm?t=1676311240\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2284090/extras/f58729f63a58d866f173e6ca6b8f414c.mp4?t=1676311240\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
